r app.\n\n*Mihir*\n*Ontrip*\n1. complete the ontrip project today the mobile application make it proper \nand implement proper notification for chat community .provide the option for notification \nseeting on/off features.\n2. Yugen will work on the backend side of ontrip so cordinate with him . \n\n*Parth*\n1. For the calling agent, connect with Arpit sir to understand the cost and requirements. After that, start the implementation. Also, share the update of the mattress-related project with Arpit sir and take acknowledgement once it is completed.\n2. website busilder in biz360 create a BOT that bot can give the website details and website owner details .\neverything about website the bot can give him.\n\n*Anishree*\n1. Test the Homenest application as a customer perspective apk take from \n    akshaya also check their admin panel . [ref: Urban app]\n\n*Jagannath*\n1. As per the meeting with Suffian sir and the decided deadlines, prepare a detailed report on how and by when the project will be completed.\n2. make it complete the Maestros project today.\n3. Share the status of the railway project with Arpit sir, including whether the Indian voice translation is completed or not and all the pending work from your side create the document and submit to the arpit sir.\n\n*Akshaya*\n1. Complete all the remaining tasks in the HomeNest project.\n2. Perform end-to-end testing after clearing existing data.\n3. Validate the complete flow step by step:\n4. Create fresh data and verify all modules\n5. Perform bookings and ensure the process works correctly\n6. Apply coupons and verify discount functionality\n7. Check booking history and ensure accurate data display\n8. Test chat functionality and confirm proper communication flow from 120363328765739816@g.us","timestamp":"2026-04-23 11:18:25"}
